creator: Sarif Tech Ltd
descriptionHtml:
Spotlight VR is a live events experience for Oculus and Android devices.

From live music events with real musicians to Art Exhibitions showcasing one of our featured Artists to Speed Dating events, there'll always be something to enjoy.

Using our green screen technology, live artists will feel like they're with you in VR!

Our venues can be used for all kinds of events, but here's just a few exciting events you'll find:

- Socialise in any of our public rooms 24 hours a day
- Join our live OpenMic events in our British pub
- Wander our museums and enjoy one of our featured Artists work
- Attend Speed Dating events and make new connections
- Take part in our very own Pub Quiz
- Join friends in album listening parties
- Attend one of our cinema screens and enjoy YouTube videos or any streaming video with friends

And that's just the start. Our events can be used for all kinds of live event.

Want to take part in any of the events? Use your phone or webcam to live stream directly onto our stages!

Using our green screen technology, live artists will feel like they're with you in VR!

Our venues can be used for all kinds of events, but here's just a few exciting events you'll find:

- Socialise in any of our public rooms 24 hours a day
- Join our live OpenMic events in our British pub
- Wander our museums and enjoy one of our featured Artists work
- Attend Speed Dating events and make new connections
- Take part in our very own Pub Quiz
- Join friends in album listening parties
- Attend one of our cinema screens and enjoy YouTube videos or any streaming video with friends

And that's just the start. Our events can be used for all kinds of live event.

Want to take part in any of the events? Use your phone or webcam to live stream directly onto our stages!
